---
<div class="banner">
    <div class="item __main">
        <img src={img1.src}>
        <div class="text">
            <h1>Lorem ipsum sit amet</h1>
            <span>
            Lorem ipsu dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.
